{
  "texts": [
    "Semantic reasoning skills are also indispensable to interpret the 'coexistence of two phases' as the concurrent existence of the mentioned metallic and insulating phases.",
    "The benefits of our datasets are multi-faceted.",
    "Firstly, it is a chemical QA dataset for research purposes, encompassing a wide range of topics from basic concepts to complex chemical processes.",
    "Secondly, it requires complex reasoning and in-depth semantic analysis to deduce the answer.",
    "Thirdly, ScholarChemQA sets a new benchmark for AI in real-world, academic contexts, enhancing AI-driven exploration and discovery in chemistry."
  ]
